description:
**Special Meeting, July 27, 2012, 10am. The Oregon Board of Architect Examiners will be considering an amended proposed order in the matter of Twist Architecture Inc, David Hansen, and Kirk Callison, respondents.

The next regular meeting of the Oregon Board of Architect Examiners is August 24, 2012
